<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>
    <%= title %>
  </title>
  <link rel="stylesheet"
    href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Lora:wght@400;500;600&display=swap">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.8.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>

<body>
  <div class="about-page">
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="header">
      <div class="container">
        <nav class="navbar">
          <a href="/" class="logo">Elara Regency</a>
          <ul class="nav-links">
            <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="/rooms">Rooms</a></li>
            <li><a href="/locations">Locations</a></li>
            <li><a href="/about" class="gold-text">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="/blog">Blog</a></li>
            <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
            <% if (isLoggedIn) { %>
              <li><a href="/reservation">Reservation</a></li>
              <li><a href="/logout">Logout</a></li>
              <% } else { %>
                <li><a href="/login">Login</a></li>
                <li><a href="/register">Register</a></li>
                <% } %>
          </ul>
          <div class="hamburger">
            <div></div>
            <div></div>
            <div></div>
          </div>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Page Banner -->
    <section class="page-banner"
      style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1717687099734-4fe6563e2863?q=80&w=2671&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D'); padding: 150px 0 100px; background-size: cover; background-position: center;">
      <div class="container text-center">
        <h1>About Elara Regency</h1>
        <p>Our story of luxury, excellence, and unparalleled hospitality</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Our Story -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
          <h2>Our Story</h2>
        </div>

        <div
          style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 3rem; align-items: center;">
          <div>
            <p>Founded in 1985 by visionary hotelier Jonathan Elara, Elara Regency began with a single property in New
              York City. Jonathan's vision was simple yet ambitious: to create hotels that would redefine luxury
              hospitality by combining timeless elegance with personalized service and attention to detail.</p>
            <p>Over the decades, Elara Regency has grown from a single boutique hotel to a global luxury hospitality
              brand with properties in the world's most coveted destinations. Throughout our expansion, we have remained
              true to our founding principles, ensuring that each Elara Regency property offers the same exceptional
              experience that has become our hallmark.</p>
            <p>Today, under the leadership of CEO Victoria Elara, Jonathan's daughter, we continue to innovate and
              elevate the luxury hotel experience while honoring our rich heritage and commitment to excellence.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1529290130-4ca3753253ae?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80"
              alt="Elara Regency History" style="width: 100%; border-radius: 5px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Our Philosophy -->
    <section class="section" style="background-color: var(--dark-secondary);">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
          <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
          <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
            "Luxury is not about opulence, but about creating moments of perfection through thoughtful service and
            meticulous attention to detail."
          </p>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">â€” Jonathan Elara, Founder</p>
        </div>

        <div
          style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; margin-top: 3rem;">
          <div class="feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <i class="bi bi-gem"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Best Quality</h3>
            <p>We believe in delivering the highest quality in every aspect of our service, from the materials in our
              rooms to the ingredients in our restaurants.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <i class="bi bi-heart"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Personalized Service</h3>
            <p>We recognize that true luxury lies in personalization. Our staff is trained to anticipate and fulfill the
              unique needs of each guest.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <i class="bi bi-globe"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Cultural Authenticity</h3>
            <p>Each of our properties embraces and celebrates the culture and heritage of its location, offering guests
              an authentic experience.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <i class="bi bi-shield-check"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Sustainable Luxury</h3>
            <p>We are committed to responsible luxury, implementing sustainable practices that respect our environment
              and communities.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Leadership Team -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
          <h2>Our Leadership</h2>
        </div>

        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem;">
          <!-- CEO -->
          <div style="text-align: center;">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1573496359142-b8d87734a5a2?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80"
              alt="Victoria Elara"
              style="width: 200px; height: 200px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 50%; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            <h3>Victoria Elara</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Chief Executive Officer</p>
            <p>Victoria has led Elara Regency since 2010, continuing her father's legacy while driving innovation and
              global expansion.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- COO -->
          <div style="text-align: center;">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560250097-0b93528c311a?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80"
              alt="James Richardson"
              style="width: 200px; height: 200px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 50%; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            <h3>James Richardson</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Chief Operating Officer</p>
            <p>With over 25 years in luxury hospitality, James oversees the day-to-day operations of all Elara Regency
              properties.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- CMO -->
          <div style="text-align: center;">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580489944761-15a19d654956?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80"
              alt="Sophia Chen"
              style="width: 200px; height: 200px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 50%; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            <h3>Sophia Chen</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Chief Marketing Officer</p>
            <p>Sophia leads our global marketing strategy, ensuring the Elara Regency brand remains synonymous with
              luxury and excellence.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Head Chef -->
          <div style="text-align: center;">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1583394838336-acd977736f90?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80"
              alt="Marco Rossi"
              style="width: 200px; height: 200px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 50%; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            <h3>Marco Rossi</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Global Culinary Director</p>
            <p>A Michelin-starred chef, Marco oversees the culinary direction of all Elara Regency restaurants
              worldwide.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Awards & Recognition -->
    <section class="section" style="background-color: var(--dark-secondary);">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
          <h2>Awards & Recognition</h2>
        </div>

        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem;">
          <div class="feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <i class="bi bi-trophy"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>World's Leading Luxury Hotel Brand</h3>
            <p>World Travel Awards, 2020-2023</p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <i class="bi bi-star"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Five-Star Rating</h3>
            <p>Forbes Travel Guide, All Properties, 2018-2023</p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <i class="bi bi-award"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Best Hotel Group Worldwide</h3>
            <p>Luxury Travel Intelligence, 2021-2023</p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <i class="bi bi-globe2"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>World's Most Sustainable Luxury Hotel Chain</h3>
            <p>Global Sustainable Tourism Council, 2022</p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <i class="bi bi-cup-hot"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Best Hotel Dining Experience</h3>
            <p>International Culinary Excellence Awards, 2019-2023</p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <i class="bi bi-people"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Best Employer in Hospitality</h3>
            <p>Hospitality Global, 2020-2023</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Our Commitment -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
          <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
        </div>

        <div
          style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 3rem; align-items: center;">
          <div>
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1532375810709-75b1da00537c?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80"
              alt="Sustainability Initiatives" style="width: 100%; border-radius: 5px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);">
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 style="color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Sustainability</h3>
            <p>At Elara Regency, we believe that luxury and sustainability can and must coexist. Our commitment to
              environmental stewardship is reflected in every aspect of our operations, from energy-efficient buildings
              to waste reduction programs and locally sourced ingredients in our restaurants.</p>

            <h3 style="color: var(--gold); margin: 1.5rem 0 1rem;">Community</h3>
            <p>We are dedicated to making a positive impact in the communities where we operate. Through the Elara
              Foundation, we support local education, arts, and environmental initiatives, and we prioritize hiring and
              sourcing locally whenever possible.</p>

            <h3 style="color: var(--gold); margin: 1.5rem 0 1rem;">Diversity & Inclusion</h3>
            <p>We celebrate diversity in our workforce and are committed to creating an inclusive environment where all
              employees and guests feel valued and respected, regardless of background, identity, or ability.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Join Our Team -->
    <section class="section" style="background-color: var(--dark-secondary);">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center">
          <h2>Join Our Team</h2>
          <p style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto 2rem;">We are always looking for passionate individuals who share
            our commitment to excellence and hospitality. Explore career opportunities with Elara Regency and be part of
            our global family.</p>
          <a href="#" class="btn">View Career Opportunities</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="footer-content">
          <div class="footer-about">
            <div class="footer-logo">Elara Regency</div>
            <p>Setting new standards in luxury hospitality across the globe with our commitment to excellence and
              personalized service.</p>
            <div class="social-links">
              <a href="#"><i class="bi bi-facebook"></i></a>
              <a href="#"><i class="bi bi-instagram"></i></a>
              <a href="#"><i class="bi bi-twitter"></i></a>
              <a href="#"><i class="bi bi-linkedin"></i></a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="footer-links">
            <h3>Quick Links</h3>
            <ul>
              <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
              <li><a href="/rooms">Rooms</a></li>
              <li><a href="/locations">Locations</a></li>
              <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
              <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="footer-links">
            <h3>Contact Us</h3>
            <ul>
              <li><i class="bi bi-geo-alt"></i> 123 Luxury Avenue, New York</li>
              <li><i class="bi bi-telephone"></i> +1 (555) 123-4567</li>
              <li><i class="bi bi-envelope"></i> info@elararegency.com</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="copyright">
          &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Elara Regency. All rights reserved.
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </div>

  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>

</html>